.br
Returns: Nothing
.br
Type: void 

.br
Parameter\fB[1]\fR: A pointer to a constant Ustr string
.br
Type\fB[1]\fR: const struct Ustr *

.br
Parameter\fB[2]\fR: Return size allocated number
.br
Type\fB[2]\fR: size_t *

.br
Parameter\fB[3]\fR: Return number of bytes used in the reference count
.br
